high_descs: Turn left and walk around the coffee table. Turn right to face the coffee table,
Pick up the statue off of the coffee table.
Turn around and walk left to the side table.
Place the statue on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Move a statue to a side table.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go around to the front of the coffee table in front of you.
Pick up the statue to the left of the newspaper on the table.
Turn to your left and go to the end table to the left of the couch across from you.
Place the statue on the right front corner of the end table.
anns.task_desc: Put the statue from the coffee table on the end table.

high_descs: Head straight to the glass coffee table with the red bowl and man statue.
Pick up the man statue from the glass coffee table.
Turn left and head to the black side table next to the couch.
Place the man statue on the black side table.
anns.task_desc: To move the man statue to the black side table.
